title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4606.14 - Identification number required
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4606.14 - Identification number required

State Regulations

Every authorized organization desiring to apply for a
license as a games of chance lessor shall have previously filed an application
for an identification number on form 1A Application for Registration and

Identification Number, as prescribed by the commission, and secured an
identification number from the commission. The provisions of this section do
not require an authorized organization that has received an identification
number to conduct games of chance from the commission to obtain another
identification number to become an authorized games of chance
lessor. Notes
